  "A mechanical engineer designs a lever system where input forces (F1, F2) produce output displacements (d1, d2) via d = AF. She measures: input (1,0) gives displacement (3,1) and input (0,1) gives displacement (1,2). What displacement results from input force (2,3)?": "",
