  "A civil engineer models traffic flow at two intersections. The flow transformation is T(x,y) = (0.7x + 0.3y, 0.4x + 0.6y) where x and y are incoming car counts. Starting with 1000 cars at each intersection, what are the predicted flows after one time step?": "",
